# PINN-CFD Project

## ğŸ“Œ Overview
This project integrates **Physics-Informed Neural Networks (PINNs)** with **Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD)** for solving steady-state Navierâ€“Stokes and energy equations.  
It supports mesh-based simulations, thermodynamic/transport properties, and optional chemical kinetics.

